{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Pat Mitchell: You have brought us images from the Yemen Times."},{"time":4000,"text":"And take us through those,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and introduce us to another Yemen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10000,"text":"Nadia Al-Sakkaf: Well, I'm glad to be here."},{"time":12000,"text":"And I would like to share with you all"},{"time":14000,"text":"some of the pictures that are happening today in Yemen."},{"time":17000,"text":"This picture shows a revolution"},{"time":19000,"text":"started by women,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and it shows women and men"},{"time":24000,"text":"leading a mixed protest."},{"time":26000,"text":"The other picture"},{"time":28000,"text":"is the popularity of the real need for change."},{"time":32000,"text":"So many people are there."},{"time":34000,"text":"The intensity of the upspring."},{"time":38000,"text":"This picture shows that the revolution"},{"time":40000,"text":"has allowed opportunities for training,"},{"time":42000,"text":"for education."},{"time":44000,"text":"These women are learning about first aid"},{"time":46000,"text":"and their rights according to the constitution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"I love this picture."},{"time":51000,"text":"I just wanted to show"},{"time":53000,"text":"that over 60 percent of the Yemeni population"},{"time":55000,"text":"are 15 years and below."},{"time":57000,"text":"And they were excluded from decision-making,"},{"time":59000,"text":"and now they are in the forefront of the news,"},{"time":62000,"text":"raising the flag."},{"time":64000,"text":"English --"},{"time":66000,"text":"you will see, this is jeans"},{"time":68000,"text":"and tights,"},{"time":70000,"text":"and an English expression --"},{"time":73000,"text":"the ability to share with the world"},{"time":76000,"text":"what is going on in our own country."},{"time":79000,"text":"And expression also,"},{"time":82000,"text":"it has brought talents."},{"time":84000,"text":"Yemenis are using cartoons"},{"time":86000,"text":"and art,"},{"time":89000,"text":"paintings, comics,"},{"time":91000,"text":"to tell the world and each other"},{"time":93000,"text":"about what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"Obviously, there's always the dark side of it."},{"time":98000,"text":"And this is just one of the less-gruesome pictures"},{"time":101000,"text":"of the revolution"},{"time":103000,"text":"and the cost that we have to pay."},{"time":105000,"text":"The solidarity"},{"time":107000,"text":"of millions of Yemenis across the country"},{"time":109000,"text":"just demanding the one thing."},{"time":111000,"text":"And finally, lots of people are saying"},{"time":113000,"text":"that Yemen's revolution"},{"time":115000,"text":"is going to break the country."},{"time":117000,"text":"Is it going to be so many different countries?"},{"time":119000,"text":"Is it going to be another Somalia?"},{"time":121000,"text":"But we want to tell the world that, no,"},{"time":123000,"text":"under the one flag, we'll still remain as Yemeni people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"PM: Thank you for those images, Nadia."},{"time":130000,"text":"And they do, in many ways,"},{"time":132000,"text":"tell a different story"},{"time":134000,"text":"than the story of Yemen,"},{"time":136000,"text":"the one that is often in the news."},{"time":138000,"text":"And yet, you yourself"},{"time":140000,"text":"defy all those characterizations."},{"time":142000,"text":"So let's talk about the personal story for a moment."},{"time":146000,"text":"Your father is murdered."},{"time":149000,"text":"The Yemen Times already has"},{"time":151000,"text":"a strong reputation in Yemen"},{"time":154000,"text":"as an independent English language newspaper."},{"time":158000,"text":"How did you then"},{"time":160000,"text":"make the decision and assume the responsibilities"},{"time":162000,"text":"of running a newspaper,"},{"time":164000,"text":"especially in such times of conflict?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"NA: Well, let me first warn you"},{"time":169000,"text":"that I'm not the traditional Yemeni girl."},{"time":172000,"text":"I've guessed you've already noticed this by now."},{"time":174000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":176000,"text":"In Yemen, most women are veiled"},{"time":178000,"text":"and they are sitting behind doors"},{"time":181000,"text":"and not very much part of the public life."},{"time":183000,"text":"But there's so much potential."},{"time":185000,"text":"I wish I could show you my Yemen."},{"time":188000,"text":"I wish you could see"},{"time":190000,"text":"Yemen through my eyes."},{"time":192000,"text":"Then you would know"},{"time":194000,"text":"that there's so much to it."},{"time":196000,"text":"And I was privileged because I was born into a family,"},{"time":199000,"text":"my father would always encourage the boys and the girls."},{"time":203000,"text":"He would say we are equal."},{"time":206000,"text":"And he was such an extraordinary man."},{"time":209000,"text":"And even my mother -- I owe it to my family."},{"time":212000,"text":"A story:"},{"time":214000,"text":"I studied in India."},{"time":216000,"text":"And in my third year, I started becoming confused"},{"time":219000,"text":"because I was Yemeni,"},{"time":221000,"text":"but I was also mixing up"},{"time":223000,"text":"with a lot of my friends in college."},{"time":225000,"text":"And I went back home and I said,"},{"time":228000,"text":"\"Daddy, I don't know who I am."},{"time":230000,"text":"I'm not a Yemeni; I'm not an Indian.\""},{"time":232000,"text":"And he said, \"You are the bridge.\""},{"time":234000,"text":"And that is something I will keep in my heart forever."},{"time":238000,"text":"So since then I've been the bridge,"},{"time":240000,"text":"and a lot of people have walked over me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"PM: I don't think so. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"NA: But it just helps tell"},{"time":249000,"text":"that some people are change agents"},{"time":251000,"text":"in the society."},{"time":253000,"text":"And when I became editor-in-chief"},{"time":255000,"text":"after my brother actually --"},{"time":257000,"text":"my father passed away in 1999,"},{"time":259000,"text":"and then my brother until 2005 --"},{"time":261000,"text":"and everybody was betting that I will not be able to do it."},{"time":264000,"text":"\"What's this young girl coming in and showing off"},{"time":267000,"text":"because it's her family business,\" or something."},{"time":270000,"text":"It was very hard at first."},{"time":272000,"text":"I didn't want to clash with people."},{"time":274000,"text":"But with all due respect"},{"time":276000,"text":"to all the men, and the older men especially,"},{"time":279000,"text":"they did not want me around."},{"time":282000,"text":"It was very hard, you know,"},{"time":284000,"text":"to impose my authority."},{"time":288000,"text":"But a woman's got to do what a woman's got to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"And in the first year,"},{"time":299000,"text":"I had to fire half of the men."},{"time":301000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":303000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":307000,"text":"Brought in more women."},{"time":310000,"text":"Brought in younger men."},{"time":312000,"text":"And we have a more gender-balanced newsroom today."},{"time":316000,"text":"The other thing is that it's about professionalism."},{"time":319000,"text":"It's about proving who you are and what you can do."},{"time":322000,"text":"And I don't know if I'm going to be boasting now,"},{"time":325000,"text":"but in 2006 alone,"},{"time":328000,"text":"we won three international awards."},{"time":330000,"text":"One of them is the IPI"},{"time":332000,"text":"Free Media Pioneer Award."},{"time":334000,"text":"So that was the answer"},{"time":336000,"text":"to all the Yemeni people."},{"time":338000,"text":"And I want to score a point here,"},{"time":340000,"text":"because my husband is in the room over there."},{"time":342000,"text":"If you could please stand up, [unclear]."},{"time":346000,"text":"He has been very supportive of me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"PM: And we should point out"},{"time":355000,"text":"that he works with you as well at the paper."},{"time":358000,"text":"But in assuming this responsibility"},{"time":360000,"text":"and going about it as you have,"},{"time":362000,"text":"you have become a bridge"},{"time":364000,"text":"between an older and traditional society"},{"time":368000,"text":"and the one that you are now creating at the paper."},{"time":371000,"text":"And so along with changing who worked there,"},{"time":374000,"text":"you must have come up against another positioning"},{"time":377000,"text":"that we always run into, in particular with women,"},{"time":380000,"text":"and it has to do with outside image,"},{"time":383000,"text":"dress, the veiled woman."},{"time":385000,"text":"So how have you dealt with this"},{"time":387000,"text":"on a personal level"},{"time":389000,"text":"as well as the women who worked for you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"NA: As you know,"},{"time":393000,"text":"the image of a lot of Yemeni women is a lot of black"},{"time":395000,"text":"and covered, veiled women."},{"time":397000,"text":"And this is true."},{"time":399000,"text":"And a lot of it is"},{"time":401000,"text":"because women are not able, are not free,"},{"time":403000,"text":"to show their face to their self."},{"time":405000,"text":"It's a lot of traditional imposing"},{"time":407000,"text":"coming by authority figures"},{"time":409000,"text":"such as the men, the grandparents and so on."},{"time":412000,"text":"And it's economic empowerment"},{"time":414000,"text":"and the ability for a woman to say,"},{"time":416000,"text":"\"I am as much contributing to this family, or more,"},{"time":419000,"text":"than you are.\""},{"time":421000,"text":"And the more empowered the women become,"},{"time":425000,"text":"the more they are able to remove the veil, for example,"},{"time":428000,"text":"or to drive their own car"},{"time":430000,"text":"or to have a job or to be able to travel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"So the other face of Yemen"},{"time":435000,"text":"is actually one"},{"time":437000,"text":"that lies behind the veil,"},{"time":439000,"text":"and it's economic empowerment mostly"},{"time":442000,"text":"that allows the woman to just uncover it."},{"time":444000,"text":"And I have done this throughout my work."},{"time":447000,"text":"I've tried to encourage young girls."},{"time":449000,"text":"We started with, you can take it off in the office."},{"time":453000,"text":"And then after that, you can take it off on assignments."},{"time":456000,"text":"Because I didn't believe a journalist can be a journalist with --"},{"time":459000,"text":"how can you talk to people if you have your face covered? --"},{"time":462000,"text":"and so on; it's just a movement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"And I am a role model in Yemen."},{"time":466000,"text":"A lot of people look up to me."},{"time":468000,"text":"A lot of young girls look up to me."},{"time":470000,"text":"And I need to prove to them that, yes, you can still be married,"},{"time":472000,"text":"you can still be a mother,"},{"time":474000,"text":"and you can still be respected within the society,"},{"time":476000,"text":"but at the same time,"},{"time":478000,"text":"that doesn't mean you [should] just be one of the crowd."},{"time":481000,"text":"You can be yourself and have your face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484000,"text":"PM: But by putting yourself personally out there --"},{"time":488000,"text":"both projecting a different image"},{"time":490000,"text":"of Yemeni women,"},{"time":492000,"text":"but also what you have made possible"},{"time":494000,"text":"for the women who work at the paper --"},{"time":497000,"text":"has this put you in personal danger?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"NA: Well the Yemen Times, across 20 years,"},{"time":504000,"text":"has been through so much."},{"time":506000,"text":"We've suffered prosecution;"},{"time":508000,"text":"the paper was closed down more than three times."},{"time":510000,"text":"It's an independent newspaper,"},{"time":513000,"text":"but tell that to the people in charge."},{"time":515000,"text":"They think that if there's anything against them,"},{"time":518000,"text":"then we are being an opposition newspaper."},{"time":522000,"text":"And very, very difficult times."},{"time":525000,"text":"Some of my reporters were arrested."},{"time":527000,"text":"We had some court cases."},{"time":529000,"text":"My father was assassinated."},{"time":531000,"text":"Today, we are in a much better situation."},{"time":534000,"text":"We've created the credibility."},{"time":536000,"text":"And in times of revolution or change like today,"},{"time":539000,"text":"it is very important for independent media to have a voice."},{"time":543000,"text":"It's very important"},{"time":545000,"text":"for you to go to YemenTimes.com,"},{"time":547000,"text":"and it's very important"},{"time":549000,"text":"to listen to our voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"And this is probably something"},{"time":554000,"text":"I'm going to share with you"},{"time":556000,"text":"in Western media probably --"},{"time":558000,"text":"and how there's a lot of stereotypes --"},{"time":562000,"text":"thinking of Yemen in one single frame:"},{"time":565000,"text":"this is what Yemen is all about."},{"time":568000,"text":"And that's not fair."},{"time":570000,"text":"It's not fair for me; it's not fair for my country."},{"time":572000,"text":"A lot of reporters come to Yemen"},{"time":574000,"text":"and they want to write a story on Al-Qaeda or terrorism."},{"time":577000,"text":"And I just wanted to share with you:"},{"time":581000,"text":"there's one reporter that came."},{"time":583000,"text":"He wanted to do a documentary"},{"time":585000,"text":"on what his editors wanted."},{"time":589000,"text":"And he ended up writing about a story that even surprised me --"},{"time":592000,"text":"hip hop --"},{"time":594000,"text":"that there are young Yemeni men"},{"time":597000,"text":"who express themselves"},{"time":599000,"text":"through dancing and puchu puchu."},{"time":602000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":604000,"text":"That thing. (PM: Rap. Break dancing.)"},{"time":607000,"text":"Yeah, break dancing."},{"time":609000,"text":"I'm not so old."},{"time":612000,"text":"I'm just not in touch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"PM: Yes, you are."},{"time":621000,"text":"Actually, that's a documentary"},{"time":623000,"text":"that's available online; the video's online."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626000,"text":"NA: ShaketheDust.org."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628000,"text":"PM: \"Shake the Dust.\" (NA: \"Shake the Dust.\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631000,"text":"PM: ShaketheDust.org."},{"time":633000,"text":"And it definitely does give a different image of Yemen."},{"time":636000,"text":"You spoke about the responsibility of the press."},{"time":639000,"text":"And certainly, when we look"},{"time":642000,"text":"at the ways in which we have separated ourselves from others"},{"time":645000,"text":"and we've created fear"},{"time":647000,"text":"and danger,"},{"time":649000,"text":"often from lack of knowledge,"},{"time":651000,"text":"lack of real understanding,"},{"time":653000,"text":"how do you see"},{"time":655000,"text":"the way that the Western press in particular"},{"time":658000,"text":"is covering this and all other stories out of the region,"},{"time":661000,"text":"but in particular, in your country?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663000,"text":"NA: Well there is a saying that says,"},{"time":666000,"text":"\"You fear what you don't know,"},{"time":668000,"text":"and you hate what you fear.\""},{"time":671000,"text":"So it's about the lack of research, basically."},{"time":674000,"text":"It's almost, \"Do your homework,\" --"},{"time":677000,"text":"some involvement."},{"time":679000,"text":"And you cannot do parachute reporting --"},{"time":682000,"text":"just jump into a country for two days"},{"time":685000,"text":"and think that you've done your homework and a story."},{"time":688000,"text":"So I wish"},{"time":690000,"text":"that the world would know my Yemen,"},{"time":692000,"text":"my country, my people."},{"time":695000,"text":"I am an example, and there are others like me."},{"time":698000,"text":"We may not be that many,"},{"time":700000,"text":"but if we are promoted"},{"time":702000,"text":"as a good, positive example,"},{"time":705000,"text":"there will be others -- men and women --"},{"time":708000,"text":"who can eventually bridge the gap --"},{"time":711000,"text":"again, coming to the bridge --"},{"time":713000,"text":"between Yemen and the world"},{"time":715000,"text":"and telling first"},{"time":717000,"text":"about recognition"},{"time":719000,"text":"and then about communication"},{"time":721000,"text":"and compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724000,"text":"I think Yemen is going to be"},{"time":726000,"text":"in a very bad situation"},{"time":729000,"text":"in the next two or three years."},{"time":731000,"text":"It's natural."},{"time":733000,"text":"But after the two years, which is a price we are willing to pay,"},{"time":736000,"text":"we are going to stand up again on our feet,"},{"time":739000,"text":"but in the new Yemen"},{"time":741000,"text":"with a younger and more empowered people --"},{"time":744000,"text":"democratic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":754000,"text":"PM: Nadia, I think you've just given us"},{"time":756000,"text":"a very different view of Yemen."},{"time":759000,"text":"And certainly you yourself and what you do"},{"time":762000,"text":"have given us a view of the future"},{"time":765000,"text":"that we will embrace"},{"time":768000,"text":"and be grateful for."},{"time":770000,"text":"And the very best of luck to you."},{"time":772000,"text":"YemenTimes.com."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775000,"text":"NA: On Twitter also."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778000,"text":"PM: So you are plugged in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}